{"id":"f8cbc509-689c-4528-a1aa-5bbd675fa1d6","name":"Vespra [ALT]","description":"<p>You and Vespra are forced to fight for the crowds of wasps who watch in excitement. One fights for freedom, while the other fights for honor. Vespra may be in her younger years, but don't mistake her skills. They're still as potent as ever.</p><p></p><p>Before the Great Heroes were ever 'Heros', they reside in their home towns, scattered across their own unique landscapes and biomes. However, there's more to the land than the Great Heroes. Explore the nations across the land and discover what they bring to this world!</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Other Inhabitants</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/458aa6f3-f00a-4cba-ac31-b230f20002ca_character-fiend\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Fiend</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/fb9936a6-11a9-442e-82a2-acd5ff43dc5d_character-tenshi\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Tenshi</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4ebc765e-5058-48a7-a500-6f977c89c584_character-winifred\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Winifred</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d74fb5f4-365c-48b6-904f-10ccb2ca7d10_character-brynn-alt\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Brynn</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6ba07ea2-a805-42bf-8afa-d11041a4452d_character-traitor\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Traitor</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1c9edf45-6371-4593-b6fc-7e0b81b7adc6_character-azrina\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Azrina</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f5fa4770-de3d-4c1b-978e-d47783a8a